        "shortDescription": "We are back for our Monday Show to bring you hours of amazing aviation footage from the best venue for plane spotting in the UK, Manchester Airport. We will bring you some amazing up close action featuring amazing aircraft from Emirates 777, Etihad, Cathay Pacific, TUI, Virgin Atlantic and many many more!! \nOne thing for sure is that there will be plenty of planes for you to enjoy!!\nAs always the stream will be starting at silly o'clock aka 0615 BST and I hope to see you there.\n\nBuy Me A Kebab\nhttps://www.buymeacoffee.com/thinkplanes\n\nManchester Airport Plane Spotting Guide:\nhttps://youtu.be/2CUeF0s2bNw?si=Ej-OAv7OmNOVilAX\n\nEmail: thinkplanes@gmail.com \n\nFor links to our socials, email and amazon store front:\nhttps://linktr.ee/thinkplanes \n......................\n\nIf you’re anything like me, there’s nothing better than watching planes up close at Manchester Airport feeling that buzz when an Emirates A380 touches down or a Ryanair 737 lifts off right before your eyes. In today’s Think Planes live stream, we’ve got all the action from runway to the clouds (normally grey ones in Manchester!)  Live plane spotting, real-time arrivals and departures, and behind-the-scenes aviation insights. Whether you’re a hardcore avgeek or just love the thrill of live airport action, grab your coffee, say hello in the chat, and let’s enjoy the skies together!\n\n#manchesterairport #planespotting #aviation \n.........................\nJoin this channel to get access to perks:\nhttps://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGrS7fwPECc1Z2w146Ku3vw/join",
